      • setCurrentQuestion

        public boolean setCurrentQuestion(java.lang.String filename,
                                  java.lang.String answer)
        Sets a new Question for the Session. Loads image via filename and sets the correct answer to be that of the inputed string. Starts by ending previous question by making it into a questiondata object. Then changes all clients lastVote to null.
        Parameters:
        filename - The image file to be loaded
        answer - The answer string to be accepted
        Returns:
        True if loads properly, False if image fails

      • addClient

        public boolean addClient(java.lang.String ID,
                         java.lang.String IP)
        Adds a new client to the session's client list with their ID and IP. If the ID's are the same, but the IP's differ it rejects it. If the IP's are the same, but the ID's differ it rejects it. If its entirely new, then it accepts it. If the IP's are the same, and the ID's are the same, remove the old instance and add this new one.
        Parameters:
        ID - - the new client's ID
        IP - - The new client's IP
        Returns:
        - True if accepted, False if rejected

        public boolean addClientVote(java.lang.String clientID,
